---
/**
 * Persistent satire disclaimer banner fixed to bottom of viewport.
 * Links to a verification/methodology page.
 */
---

<div
  class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-navy-900 border-t-2 border-gold-500"
  role="contentinfo"
  aria-label="Satire disclaimer"
>
  <div class="py-2 px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-cream-200 font-serif italic">
      This is satire. Some of it's real. We'll let you figure out which.
      <a
        href="/about#verify"
        class="ml-2 text-cream-100 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors not-italic"
      >
        Verify it yourself
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
